一啲勸唔聽既人歸納做鬼<br />\n真係唔好再指責落去 如果唔係場運動唔洗落去<br />\n我覺得暫時大家咁分歧既時候唔應該過度提倡各有各做<br />\n畢竟真係會有人比情緒 慾望沖昏頭腦 唔聽勸<br />\n好心做壞事 然後就好容易出現屌鬼既情況<br />\n「各有各做」開始變左唔聽人講既擋箭牌<br />\n令我地見到唔應該發生既事都阻住唔到"},{"pid":"f7eb351fcbe1d9a151c39842303dde65777c97d6","tid":1461932,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分化</span> 保持警覺</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">小心暗黑兵法劇本：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n內耗：內部分化示威者、<br />\n酷刑威嚇被捕人士、<br />\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、<br />\n逐步暴力鎮壓 拘捕前線瓦解、<br />\n文宣抹黑 嫁禍 插贜示威者、<br />\n暗殺第一滴血 逆轉民意 國際譴責、<br />\n人民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、<br />\n中立派賺錢派 政治疲勞、<br />\n鼓吹經濟下滑 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、<br />\n拖延分散擊破 學季始開、<br />\n雨傘結局  清算開始<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">十項推文 試著說<br />\n勿忘612、721、811</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">811警暴連環<br />\n⒈蓄意謀殺女救護 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>布袋鉛彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>瞄準</strong></span>眼球 永久失明 面骨碎裂、<br />\n⒉插贜竹枝 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">造偽證</span></strong> 誣陷被捕者、<br />\n⒊地鐡<strong>站內 水平發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣、<br />\n⒋警<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">喬裝示威者 發動衝擊</span></strong>縱火、<br />\n⒌普通話<strong>軍人 多處滲透</strong>武統、<br />\n⒍<strong>一米內行刑 掃射</strong>胡椒彈槍、險釀電梯<strong>人踩人</strong>、<br />\n⒎<strong>縱容黑幫</strong>橫行 毆打記者路人、<br />\n⒏濫暴<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">痛毆 重創被捕者</span></strong> 打掉門牙 血肉模糊、<br />\n⒐屋村<strong>老人民居 發射催淚彈</strong>CS神經毒氣<br />\n１０. 殘害救護員、<strong>救護舉旗警告</strong> 尖沙咀<strong>阻礙救援</strong> 違反國際人道法 屬嚴重刑事罪行</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">August 11, 2019 *** Police Brutality ***<br />\n<br />\n⒈ <strong>Macilously and unlawfully</strong> cause <strong>Greivous Bodily Harm</strong> - Gun <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Aims for the head</strong></span>: <br />\n    <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Shooting lean-filled pellet round directly to a First-aider&rsquo;s eye</strong></span>, causing grievous bodily harm including:<br />\n<strong>      - Right eyeball RUPTURED. <br />\n      - Permanent BLINDNESS. <br />\n      - Eyelids and tear ducts LACERATIONS.<br />\n      - Facial FRACTURED.</strong><br />\n⒉ <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Planting fake evidence</span></strong> on arrested protesters (putting sharp bamboo into protestors&rsquo; backpack)<br />\n⒊ <strong>Unlawfully &amp; Horizontally lauching TEARGAS canisters INDOOR</strong> (in MTR subway stations at civilians)<br />\n⒋ Officers <strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">disguised as demonstrators to take the lead</span></strong>, and incite them to violence.<br />\n⒌ Mandarin-speaking officers spotted: suspected to be <strong>Mainland China officers undercovering</strong> as HKPF.<br />\n⒍ <strong>SWEEP-SHOTTING protesters with projectiles</strong> (Pepperball Pistol) at less than 1m range. <br />\n     Shoved protesters down escalators (almost causing <strong>STAMPEDE</strong>).<br />\n⒎ <strong>Turned a blind eye towards gangsters</strong>(who support HK police) chasing up <br />\n     and <strong>beating pedestrians</strong>, reporters and protesters on streets.<br />\n⒏ Bloody arrest: <strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">Brutally beaten up arrested protester</span></strong> (protester who was under control - wrestled to the ground moaning in pain with front tooth knocked out).<br />\n⒐ <strong>Launching TEARGAS canisters</strong> in suburban area populated by old <strong>residential buildings</strong>(outside the <strong>elderly homes</strong>, community centers, and nearby residences). Pepper-sprayed residences&rsquo; on-duty security guards.<br />\n１０. (Serious Criminal Offence) <strong>Obstruction of medical care</strong> - in violation of the International Humanitarian Law. <strong>First-aider raising the Flag for Warning</strong> in TST.<br />\n</span>"}]}